define growlight -1758710260
alias 105IsLightOn r10 #control alias 105count r11 alias 85IsLightOn r8 alias 85count r9 alias 103IsLightOn r6 alias 103count r7 alias 82IsLightOn r4 alias 82count r5
start: yield # Get the current status of the growlights lbn 105IsLightOn growlight HASH("105") On 2 lbn 85IsLightOn growlight HASH("85") On 2 lbn 103IsLightOn growlight HASH("103") On 2 lbn 82IsLightOn growlight HASH("82") On 2 # If the lightson is on, go to the specific loop to check the time counter for 10 minutes on, 5 minutes off bgtzal 105IsLightOn 105LightOnLoop beqzal 105IsLightOn 105LightOffLoop add 105count 105count 1
# Same for 8 minutes on, 5 minutes off bgtzal 85IsLightOn 85LightOnLoop beqzal 85IsLightOn 85LightOffLoop add 85count 85count 1
# Same for 9 minutes on, 5 minutes off bgtzal 103IsLightOn 103LightOnLoop beqzal 103IsLightOn 103LightOffLoop add 103count 103count 1
# Same for 7 minutes on, 5 minutes off bgtzal 82IsLightOn 82LightOnLoop beqzal 82IsLightOn 82LightOffLoop add 82count 82count 1 j start
105LightOnLoop: # Go back if it's below the target ble 105count 1200 ra # If it's above the target value, set the light off sbn growlight HASH("105") On 0 # Change the control and reset the counter move 105IsLightOn 0 move 105count 0 j ra
105LightOffLoop: # Go back if it's below the target ble 105count 600 ra # If it's above the target value, set the light on sbn growlight HASH("105") On 1 # Change the control and reset the counter move 105IsLightOn 1 move 105count 0 j ra
85LightOnLoop: # Go back if it's below the target ble 85count 960 ra # If it's above the target value, set the light off sbn growlight HASH("85") On 0 # Change the control and reset the counter move 85IsLightOn 0 move 85count 0 j ra
85LightOffLoop: # Go back if it's below the target ble 85count 600 ra # If it's above the target value, set the light on sbn growlight HASH("85") On 1 # Change the control and reset the counter move 85IsLightOn 1 move 85count 0 j ra
103LightOnLoop: # Go back if it's below the target ble 103count 1200 ra # If it's above the target value, set the light off sbn growlight HASH("103") On 0 # Change the control and reset the counter move 103IsLightOn 0 move 103count 0 j ra
103LightOffLoop: # Go back if it's below the target ble 103count 400 ra # If it's above the target value, set the light on sbn growlight HASH("103") On 1 # Change the control and reset the counter move 103IsLightOn 1 move 103count 0 j ra
82LightOnLoop: # Go back if it's below the target ble 82count 1000 ra # If it's above the target value, set the light off sbn growlight HASH("82") On 0 # Change the control and reset the counter move 82IsLightOn 0 move 82count 0 j ra
82LightOffLoop: # Go back if it's below the target ble 82count 200 ra # If it's above the target value, set the light on sbn growlight HASH("82") On 1 # Change the control and reset the counter move 82IsLightOn 1 move 82count 0 j ra

alias combCent d0 alias diodeSlide d1
define MINRPM 400 define MAXSTRESS 100 define STRESSHIGH 80 define STRESSCOOL 10 define MAXIMUM 200 define STEP 10 define MAXPOWER 100 define MINPOWER 0 define MAXIDLE 100
setup: s combCent CombustionLimiter 0 s combCent Throttle 0 s combCent On 1 s combCent Open 0
start: yield l r0 combCent Rpm blt r0 MINRPM startup j idle
idle: sleep 10 l r0 combCent Stress bge r0 MAXSTRESS startup l r0 combCent Rpm blt r0 MINRPM startup l r0 db Setting add r0 r0 1 brlt r0 MAXIDLE 4 add r0 0 0 s db Setting r0 j unload s db Setting r0 div r0 r0 100 s diodeSlide Setting r0 j idle
unload: s combCent On 0 yield l r0 combCent Rpm bgt r0 0 unload s combCent Open 1 yield sleep 20 # wait to unload s combCent Open 0 yield s combCent On 1 yield s combCent Throttle 0 yield s combCent CombustionLimiter 0 yield j idle
startup: # test for cooldown l r0 combCent Stress sgt r0 r0 99 l r1 combCent Rpm slt r1 r1 1 and r0 r0 r1 bgtz r0 cooldown
# stress raising? l r0 combCent Stress yield sleep 1 l r9 combCent Stress sub r9 r0 r9 sltz r9 r9
l r1 combCent Throttle l r2 combCent CombustionLimiter
add r3 r1 r2 sge r3 r3 MAXIMUM l r4 combCent Rpm div r8 r4 MINRPM s diodeSlide Setting r8 sgt r4 r4 MINRPM max r3 r3 r4 bgt r3 0 idle
beqz r9 increase j startup
increase: add r1 r1 STEP min r1 r1 MAXPOWER brlt r1 MAXPOWER 2 # increment CL if TH == 100 add r2 r2 STEP min r2 r2 MAXPOWER s combCent Throttle r1 yield s combCent CombustionLimiter r2 yield j startup
cooldown: s combCent On 0 l r0 combCent Stress sgtz r0 r0 bgtz r0 cooldown j setup
